entries.femaleVariant: Think you know how things work around here, but you don't know shit.
Dolls aren't here to give you pleasure and satisfaction out of the goodness of their soul. They're workers. Their job's to generate profit.
Name and address.
Why'd you do that?
Don't know a last name.
You took her to the ripper 'stead of following orders? Didn't take you for someone with balls.
entries.maleVariant: You took her to the ripper instead of following orders? Didn't take you for someone with balls.

entries.femaleVariant: The ripper – name and address.
Looking for Evelyn Parker.
Tell me where Evelyn is.
I'm not leaving without info.
You look like a reasonable man – let's make a deal.
You don't understand what's at stake.
Don't have time for your games. Need to know where Evelyn is.
I'm not leaving till I know where Evelyn is.
They call you Woodman, right? That because you have as much charisma as a tree-stump?
All right, fine. I'll lay it on you straight.
Humor me, will ya? This particular piece of ass, out of all of them – why?
Girl you're lookin' for... Parker?
Doc Fingers on Jig-Jig Street. Sounds like a coed's wet dream.
And like all basic whores, she got what was comin'.
Hey, no clients allowed in here.
Got nobody working here by that name.
We're runnin' a skin circus here, case you haven't noticed, not a missing persons bureau.
Fine, so stand there and watch the minutes go by.
Somehow I doubt you understand the situation you're in.
Wanna find Evelyn, look there.
Well aren't you the queen of fuck-ups.
entries.maleVariant: Well aren't you the king of fuck-ups.

entries.femaleVariant: Sold her off to a ripper?
You're not helping.
Oh well... Can't say I didn't try playing nice.
Be a dear and close the door on your way out, would ya?
entries.maleVariant: Be a choom and close the door on your way out, would ya?

entries.femaleVariant: As you can see, I'm very busy.
But she used to. What happened to her?
Lemme guess, you played with the doll once or twice and now you wanna run off into the sunset?
Just keep your bloody mouth shut. I'm busy.
Situation, what situation? Think I give a cat's turd about every slut who walks through here?
entries.maleVariant: Situation, what situation? Think I give a cat's turd about every limp dick who walks through here?

entries.femaleVariant: She wasn't even that good...
She was hot, I'll give you that. But for all her delusions of grandeur, she was nothing more than a basic whore.
As will you.
She ain't here.
Get to the point.
This you talkin' it out straight? What happened to Evelyn?
Evelyn stopped bringing in profits?
Evelyn stop pullin' profit?
No denyin' that, sadly for her.
Dolls often malfunction?
They common – these kind of accidents?
Ever use tech that never broke? Didn't think so.
Behavioral chip splits you right down the middle. Some people plain lose their minds.
Got an order from up high to recycle her.
You killed her?
No. I found a ripperdoc who was willin' to take a look. Eh, said he knew something or other.
And for every one that does, there's a dozen in line to replace 'em.
Don't fuck with me.
I'm not. Goes by Fingers. Clinic's in some god-forsaken alley up on Jig-Jig Street.
For fuck's sake, I'm not runnin' a slaughterhouse here. I only recycle as a last resort. And family always gets a call, if there is any.
Think there are any daddies out there willin' to change the diapers of a brain-dead little slut on the verge of cyberpsychosis?
Saw what she did to the client. She get spiked or something?
Her chip was fuckin' rot. Believe you me, we tried to fix it. Didn't even come close.
Her chip was busted up pretty damn good.
Girl was a vegetable. Believe you me, we tried to fix it. Didn't even come close.
Probably did what all the dolls try to do – found a unicorn to set her up for life.
Eh, you can do better. Try Roxie over at booth two.
Same heart-shaped ass. Behavioral chip'll do the rest. Won't feel any difference.
Real pleasure chattin', but just where exactly d'you see this goin'?
Ehh, this conversation's starting to bore me.
I know she got hit by a netrunner.
You've been covering up her disappearance.
Your work is garbage.
I know you got hit by a runner and Evelyn was the target.
I know you been covering up what happened to her. Heard you told everyone she jetted off to Oslo.
You're a shit caretaker. Girls're vanishing into thin air and you don't know who, what, when, where, why and how?
entries.maleVariant: You're a shit caretaker. Girls're vanishing into thin air and you don't know who, what, when, why, where and how?

entries.femaleVariant: What happened after that?
I mean, you even know where Oslo is?
Tell you to fuckin' shave and clean up your act if I was your boss.
entries.maleVariant: I'd tell you to fuckin' shave and clean up your act if I was your boss.

entries.femaleVariant: Tell me something I don't know. Like, where is she?
You invested eddies in Evelyn?
You invested your own eddies to help poor unprofitable Evelyn? Please…
Hehehe, ya got me. Ripper's the one who paid me.
For a broken doll?
Well... anything's better than a bullet to the brain.
People got all kinds o' kinks. Trust me, I know, considerin' where I work.
Fingers is a real specimen, though. Got all the fetishes, even the ones you've never heard of. I'm sure he found her a nice niche, hehehe…
Better than a bullet to the brain.
You're repulsive.
People like you deserve a special place in hell.
Hehehehe, ya know, that's what every doll says. I'm startin' to like you. You lookin' for work by any chance?
Ehh... people like you need to come up with better insults.
We done here?
Now what...
Chip was busted... Could've sent her to get it patched up.
A ripper named Fingers, in a back alley for hookers... sounds like a joytoy's wet dream.
Looks like you've got a netrunner problem. I can help.
Look to me like a reasonable man. I think we can work somethin' out.
And you look to me like a psycho bitch who's never been ghosted by her belle or beau before. But go on, I'm listening.
entries.maleVariant: And you to me look like a psycho prick who's never been ghosted by his beau or belle before. But go on, I'm listening.

entries.femaleVariant: I know Night City's finest looks the other way when it comes to this eyesore. Just so happens I've got a friend on the vice squad…
entries.maleVariant: I know Night City's finest looks the other way when it comes to this eyesore. But it just so happens I've got a friend on the vice squad…

entries.femaleVariant: Friend who'd do anything if I bought him his diner breakfast. He'd just have to snap his fingers, and this place'd get turned inside out.
They wouldn't find shit.
Clouds's under Tyger Claw control, isn't it?
That's none of your fuckin' biz.
Guessin' you heard about Jotaro Shobo.
Uh, Shobo had an accident...
Doll goes missing, client gets messed up, and management's just sitting there, sucking his thumb…
Pretty strange for a place that advertises itself as one hundred per cent secure.
You gonna get to the bloody point?
Right, we're done here.
Bwahahaha… Ahh…
That so funny?
First off, I highly fucking doubt you know who my boss is. If you did, you wouldn't be calling her my "bosses."
And on second thought, think I'll take you to Maiko now. Just to see the look on her face when you tell her whatever it is you make up on the way.
She hates lying bitches as much as I do. But we all deserve a laugh, don't we?
entries.maleVariant: She hates lying assholes as much as I do. But we all deserve a laugh, don't we?

entries.femaleVariant: If I were you I'd run the cash angle. It's practically written on his face – F-R-A-U-D.
Know you've been skimmin' off this place's till. How much you klep already?
What the fuck are you talkin' about?
Talkin' about the eddies you skim from Clouds' accounts on a weekly basis.
Not skimmin' anything. I'd have to be a fool.
Doesn't matter. I'm just curious what the Tyger Claw leadership is gonna think once they find out.
Won't think anything because it ain't fuckin' true. I work with the dolls – Clouds' accounts got shit to do with me.
You sneaky little bitch.
entries.maleVariant: You sneaky little shit.

entries.femaleVariant: Kudos to you for hatchin' this one.
Listen, you fuckin' stump. You are a piece of work with your feet up on the desk, you know that? You think you're the first asshole who's tried to blow me off?
entries.maleVariant: Listen, you fuckin' stump. You're a real piece of work with your feet up on that desk, you know that? Think you're the first asshole who's tried to blow me off?

entries.femaleVariant: Why don't you just blow me? How's that?
I could also pop your head like a balloon with my bare hands.
Doubt you wanna feel me try and prove that I can.
Uugh. Pissing myself already.
What Shobo had was a very unfortunate meeting with me. Just happened to be his last.
Wouldn't want this to be your last meeting, would ya?
entries.maleVariant: You wouldn't want this to be your last meeting, would ya?

entries.femaleVariant: 'Course not. Never wanted to be anything like Shobo…
Maybe, maybe not…
Then again, every customer'd be dragged out naked, stuffed in the back of a van and hauled off to the precinct for a statement.
Think that'd be good for biz?
No.
Who're you? Whaddayou want?
Chill, keep calm. I'm lookin' for a girl.
Relax. Looking for someone.
I'm 'onna ask the questions here.
I'm 'onna ask the questions. Drop your iron and start talkin'.
And I said, drop it.
"Keep calm?" Interestin' word choice for someone who plowed through massacrin' all along the way.
Let's hear it, then.
That so?
Know you guys got hit by a runner a while back. I can make sure that never happens again.
I can see it already – headline in tomorrow's screamsheets. Got all the evidence I need, too…
Hey, we don't need to spill any ink over this. It'd just make things worse…
Looking for a girl named Evelyn Parker.
entries.maleVariant: Lookin' for a girl named Evelyn Parker.

entries.femaleVariant: You see only Tyger Claws. Got no idea who's behind them.
You've got info, I've got eddies. It's a fair trade.
You need to pull your head outta your ass. Eddies'll buy you whores here, not snitches.
I'll pay for info.
Now you do your end – how do we board up against hacks?
You have to isolate the chip's core layers.
Not telling you shit.
You'll need soft that'll isolate chip and implant receptor layers from Clouds' subnet.
That was a bluff. Can't believe you fell for it. Thought I was gonna spill, just like that?
entries.maleVariant: That was a bluff. Can't believe you fell for it. Ya thought I was gonna spill, just like that?

entries.femaleVariant: Uhhh… now in human rather than machine?
Go die in a ditch, you lying cunt.
entries.maleVariant: Go die in a ditch, you lying fuck.

entries.femaleVariant: Gonna hold out on me now? Really?
And don't come back here. Ever.
Things got outta hand, I'll admit. But cooperate, and no one else'll get hurt.
Just stay on point.
I'm not droppin' anything.
I don't negotiate with terrorists.
What? Don't tell me you forgot already. We made a deal, you're gonna stick to it.
Info's worth grands of eddies.
Go die in a ditch, you lying cunt.
entries.maleVariant: Go die in a ditch, you lying fuck.

entries.femaleVariant: At the same time, it'll keep track of and block any attempts to modify the core on the go.
Need SmartEye – latest version.
entries.maleVariant: Ya need SmartEye – latest version.

entries.femaleVariant: SmartEye, got it.
Go down to reception – they'll find you your soulmate two-point-oh in even fewer seconds than that.
What's your price?
I look like either of those to you?
An' I'll be sure to let your bosses know how you treat your customers.
Casting 'em out on the street ain't an option, either – can't risk tanking our cred.
Prolly not.
"On your way out" – was that somehow unclear to you?
I said, I'm busy.
Too bad you can't talk to dead people. Oh wait, you're doing it now. Anyway, just scour his comp.
That just might work.
You sit here on this dank hole you probably call your "office" and think you've got it made, don't ya?
Tyger Claw bosses've got their own bosses, case you didn't know. You're just too small to see 'em.
entries.maleVariant: Tyger Claw bosses've got their own bosses. In case you didn't know. You're just too small to see 'em.

entries.femaleVariant: Congrats, you read minds better than our own fucking AI. Someone get this girl a job.
entries.maleVariant: Congrats, you read minds better than our own fucking AI. Someone get this gonk a job.

entries.femaleVariant: Oh, 'cause you're such a big shot?
By who? A client?
No, outside job, some kinda crackshot netrunner. Punched through our ICE like it was cheap wallpaper.
Whatever or whoever fried her circuits, it came from outside our subnet. They played their deck like a virtuoso.
Ever stop to think who's behind the Tyger Claw puppets you call your "bosses"?
Let's just say a certain member of the Arasaka clan wouldn't be pleased if he knew something bad happened to Evelyn. And that you're the one responsible.
Wanna ask you one more thing.
Evelyn still with this Fingers creep?
Do I look like his secretary?
How'd she look to you... last time you saw her?
You weren't listenin – told you already. Now get out.
Shobo had an unlucky meeting.
I know you've been stealing.
Gonna take this to the news.
Could crush you with my bare hands.
Maybe not, but then again...
Could end you with my bare hands.
Could end you with my bare hands.
Could end you with my bare hands.
Wanna end up like Jotaro Shobo?
I'll tell the media everything.
Could call NCPD vice right now.
Your bosses should know how you treat customers.
You're higher-up than I thought.
Could end you with my bare hands.
Well, well, looks like you're higher-up than I thought.
Tit for tat – only if you help me.
Sorry, done playing nice.
Tit for tat. Wanna be net-secure? You're gonna help me find Evelyn first.
Sorry, done playing nice.
Had a look at the menu here. And no, you don't look a thing like these meat puppets.
Girl I'm lookin' for is linked to Arasaka.
Sorry, done playing nice.
You look worse than that…
Just wanna make a donation.
Told you what you looked like. Don't tell me you weren't listening?
That's the only way this is gonna work.
Lemme tell you something else…
Let's not make this harder than it has to be.
Wonder what your Tyger Claws bosses would think.
Could end you with my bare hands.
I'll tell you another thing.
Lemme tell you one more thing.
Tell you one more thing.
Lemme tell you one more thing.
Lemme tell you one more thing.
Look, we can settle this without anyone gettin' hurt.
Why make this any harder than it needs to be?
One way or another, I'll find out...
Could end you with my bare hands.
Lemme tell you one more thing.
Listen carefully – one way or another I'm gonna find her.
That's not all…
While you're at it, take the elevator. Quicker you're outta here, the better.
Way to go, Johnny.
Surely a reasonable man like yourself wouldn't mistake a donation for a bribe?
More like a joyboy's cum-rag.
You... insolent bitch.
entries.maleVariant: You... insolent fuck.

entries.femaleVariant: Know what? Spare me the tough talk. 'Bout time I asked you a question.
Well? You've already got my fucking attention.
Fucking nice of you to finally take notice.
Better think real hard where you wanna take this.
'Cause you're really startin' to piss me off.
Should ask yourself that.
And when I do, all kinds of shit is gonna happen – shit you don't wanna end up on the wrong side of.
Assume you believe your side to be the right one?
Take a wild guess.
Hell, why don't you just scan the truth from his grey, lifeless eyes? Or scour his comp.
How did she look to you?
[Open]
